Dourine, Botswana
-----------------
Information received on [and dated] 15 Feb 2016 from Dr Letlhogile Modisa, director, Veterinary Services, Ministry of Agriculture, Gaborone, Botswana

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 30 Oct 2015
Date of confirmation of the event: 10 Feb 2016
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Trypanosoma equiperdum_
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks (3)
Outbreak 1: Gasekita, Kanye, Southern
Date of start of the outbreak: 30 Oct 2015
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: village
Affected animals:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Equidae / 2 / 1 / 0 / 0 / 0
Affected population: horses grazing in communal area

